v1.0.0alpha9
------------

[jan] Fix issues with certain locales like Turkish.


------------
v1.0.0alpha8
------------

[mms] Fix generating the install path for composer packages installed within a
      Horde component.
[mms] Ignore .git directories in composer bundle directories when creating
      package.xml file.


